file.name: array-of-referenced-object.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: 'A sample object containing an array of a referenced object'
  title: 'Sample: array of referenced object'
  version: 1.3.1

components:
  schemas:

    ObjectWithArrays:
      type: object
      required:
        - group_id
        - group_name
        - contacts_schema
      properties:
        group_id:
          type: integer
          description: Some ID
          example: 3
        group_name:
          type: string
          description: Some name
          example: 'Prawns'
        remarks:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        crufts:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            required:
              - id
            properties:
              id:
                type: integer
              description:
                type: string
        contacts_schema:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ReferencedArrayObject'

    ReferencedArrayObject:
      type: object
      required:
        - email_address
      properties:
        first_name:
          type: string
        last_name:
          type: string
        email_address:
          type: string
        phone_number:
          type: string
        spam:
          type: boolean
          description: 'Send this person spam?'
